profile_summary: Detail-oriented and reliable Warehouse Assistant with a strong background in logistics and inventory management. Proven ability to handle high-volume warehouse operations, maintain accurate inventory records, and provide exceptional customer service. Recently gained valuable experience working in a fast-paced food truck environment in Melbourne, demonstrating strong multitasking skills, adaptability, and a commitment to maintaining high standards of cleanliness and organization. Committed to safety protocols and efficient operations.

description: Assisted in the preparation and serving of food to customers.
Maintained a clean and organized work environment.
Handled cash transactions and provided excellent customer service.
Managed inventory and restocked supplies as needed.
Adhered to strict food safety and hygiene protocols.
Worked effectively in a fast-paced, high-pressure environment.
achievements: Successfully maintained zero inventory discrepancies for the duration of employment.
